text: Ivanayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Takarlikovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,584 as of 2010. There are 27 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Ivanayevo
